    <h1 style="color:white; margin-bottom:16px;">PEO fit depends on your industry</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);">Workers comp rates, compliance requirements, and benefits benchmarks vary significantly by sector. We know which PEOs are strongest in each.</p>
